#North America
deserts
- Sonoran (Baja California)
- Mojave (Death Valley)
- Great Basin (Great Salt Lake)
- Chihuahuan
mountains
- Cordillera (Cascades + Rocky Mountains + Sierra Nevada + Sierra Madre)
- Appalachians
waters
- Mississippi + Missouri + Ohio + Arkansas
- Rio Grande
- Colorado (Grand Canyon + Antelope Canyon + Rainbow Bridge)
- Columbia + Snake
- Yukon
- Mackenzie (Great Bear Lake + Great Slave Lake)
- St. Lawrence + Great Lakes (Superior, Michigan, Huron, Erie, Niagara Falls, Ontario)
- Red (Lake Winnipeg)
peninsulas
- Yucatán
- Florida
- Nova Scotia
- Labrador
- Alaska
others
- Monument Valley (butte)
- El Capitan + Yosemite Falls

#South America
Isthmus of Panama + Darién Gap
deserts
- Atacama
mountains
- Andes (Lake Titicaca)
- Guiana Highlands (tepui)
waters
- Amazon + Madeira + Negro (Amazon rainforest)
- Paraná (Iguazu Falls)
- Orinoco
- Lake Maracaibo

#Africa
deserts
- Sahara
- Kalahari + Namib
- Karoo
mountains
- Atlas
- Ethiopian Highlands
- Mount Kilimanjaro
- Table Mountain
waters
- Great Rift Valley (Albert + Edward + Kivu + Tanganyika + Malawi + Turkana)
- Nile (white + blue) + Lake Victoria
- Lake Chad
- Zambezi (Victoria Falls)
- Limpopo
- Orange
- Congo
- Niger
- Volta
- Senegal
peninsulas
- Horn of Africa
others
- Ngorongoro Crater

#Asia
India
- Deccan Plateau + Ghats
- mountains: Himalayas + Karakoram
- deserts: Thar
- rivers: Indus + Ganges + Brahmaputra
Middle east
- deserts: Arabian + Syrian
- mountains: Taurus + Zagros + Alborz + Caucasus
- rivers: Euphrates + Tigris
- lakes: Van + Urmia
- peninsulas: Anatolia (Asia Minor), Arabia, Sinai
Central
- deserts: Karakum + Kyzylkum
- mountains: Hindukush + Pamir + Tian Shan + Altai
- rivers: Amu Darya + Syr Darya
- lakes: Caspian Sea + Aral Sea + Balkhash + Issyk Kul
East
- deserts: Gobi + Taklamakan
- mountains: Kunlun + Tibetan Plateau
- rivers: Yangtze + Huang He + Pearl River, Amur, Mekong + Irrawaddy
- peninsulas: Malay, Korea
North
- rivers: Ob, Yenisey, Lena
- lakes: Baikal
- peninsulas: Kamchatka

#Europe
North
- mountains: Scandinavian
- lakes: Vänern + Vättern, Onega + Ladoga, Saimaa, Peipus
- peninsulas: Scandinavian + Jutland + Kola
West
- mountains: Alps + Black Forest, Pyrenees, Apennines, Cantabrian
- peninsulas: Iberia, Italia + Calabria, Istria
East
- mountains: Carpathians, Ural
- peninsulas: Peloponnese, Crimea
